cqs: How many relations are there between no c1 and something?
How many relations exist between no c1 and something?
How many relations are described between no c1 and something?
How many relations are proposed between no c1 and something?
How many relations are available between no c1 and something?
How many things may no c1 do with something?
How many things could no c1 do with something?
How many things can no c1 do with something?
query: SELECT (COUNT(?x) AS ?cnt) WHERE { <c1> rdfs:subClassOf [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty ?x ; owl:cardinality "0"^^xsd:nonNegativeInteger ] . }
